<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent20c858cf979d4effa291c6f1d9e15182">
</div>
<p><a href="https://www.westvalleyhospital.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="West Valley Hospital">West Valley Hospital</a> (formerly Croydon Day Hospital) has great transport links; with West Croydon Rail Station, Croydon Bus Interchange and main tram interchange all less than 100 metres away. For patients visiting outpatient appointments the hospital has over 40 car parking spaces available free of charge. </p>
<p>The hospital is also located closely to the local NHS Trust with Croydon University Hospital less than a mile away.</p>
<p>Hospital facilities</p>
<ul>
<li>Two Laminar Flow Theatres</li>
<li>Dedicated Endoscopy Service</li>
<li>Full Recovery Facilities</li>
<li>Five Private Consulting Rooms</li>
<li>OP Treatment Room</li>
<li>X-Ray &amp; Ultrasound Facilities</li>
</ul>
<p>Health Care Services</p>
<ul>
<li>Outpatient Consultation</li>
<li>Day Case Surgery</li>
<li>Pharmaceutical Services</li>
<li>Diagnostics - Imaging and Endoscopy</li>
<li>Therapy</li>
<li>Physiotherapy</li>
</ul>
